# IncrementalImportTestCases
[![CloudBees](data:image/png;base64,)](https://www.cloudbees.com/)

## Purpose
This repository is used by CloudBees incremental import test cases in conjunction with internally defined tests.

## Notes about use
### Branch Names
Branch names represent different test data sets.  It is best if the branch name is equivalent to a test case name.  For Groovy Spock framework based tests that would be the class name plus the specification name.  For java/groovy based tests that would be the class name plus the method name.

### Commits in a branch
Incremental import compares commit IDs as a way to have git compute a change list.
For this reason _*BE CAREFUL*_ copying this repository; you may lose commits or at the least have the commit IDs change.
